{"tid":1267562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：林鄭道歉令警隊士氣空前低落","createTime":"2019-06-30T03:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T03:41:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"83c4e854b2d3d39b7472915e6a4f082ff5f558ff","tid":1267562,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190630/s00001/7d977f26f882a473526d7cfbeeb2a90f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190630%2Fs00001%2F7d977f26f882a473526d7cfbeeb2a90f.jpg&h=f53e006d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府推動《逃犯條例》修訂觸發多場大規模示威遊行，亦令部分警民關係緊張。發起今午（30日）在金鐘添馬公園舉行「撐警隊 反暴力」集會的新界西立法會議員何君堯，在今日香港電台節目《給香港的信》中表示，特首林鄭月娥早前就修例作公開道歉，「反令香港警務處的無力感和士氣落入空前最低（Her apology, however, left the Hong Kong Police Department impotent and morale at an all-time low.）」。何君堯認為，在當前激進政治氛圍下，香港警隊更需公眾支持，「我們也欠警隊一個大大的感謝（we owe a big thanks to the police force)」。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯又表示，民主派向公眾危言聳聽，令他們反對修例，以至據稱有200萬人成為他們「謊言的受害者（fallen victim to their lies）」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今午撐警集會主辦方昨（29日）在fb提醒，「為照顧進入集會範圍的黑色衣著朋友不會因過熱中暑」，和為免戴口罩到場的朋友會令「現場出席人士感染」，會分別安排義工在旁照顧他們到集會完場，和邀請他們到場內的急救站。"},{"pid":"0986b305b68d522726880fcaba33fbf8203bc760","tid":1267562,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:04:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190630/s00001/1561860757153/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190630%2Fs00001%2F1561860757153%2F&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=48d5daab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190630%2Fs00001%2F1561860757153%2F&h=dd611b7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190630/s00001/1561860757153/</a>"},{"pid":"98ce926a348f4b4b23e184b8812c733be1b98348","tid":1267562,"uid":5680,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mkv6YRF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmkv6YRF.gif&h=138e054c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌撚醒你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549174330114ed7cc4783d3efdfc6b171271c057","tid":1267562,"uid":247892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"個撚個番工唔帶腦<br />\n呢份工阿豬阿狗都做得啦"},{"pid":"177839f6167ca84f7e67ba97e374e85aa0648baf","tid":1267562,"uid":19947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"不撚知所謂"},{"pid":"4eac4c1f6b9edb698e34ad718f9406739c992334","tid":1267562,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"何妖用返當年禿頭雄果招<br />\n催眠班狗仔等佢地以為自己點做都係岩既"}]}